title: MSI Everything But The Show
description:
This is my first torrent upload ever, so hopefully I've done everything right (please be kind).

I couldn't find this anywhere, and since I had to scan this for somebody anyway, I figured I'd put this up online for the BT community. So, for those of you who couldn't get it on Kickstarter or can't afford it or w/e, here it is, Mindless Self Indulgence's Kickstarter book, scanned the best I possibly could without dismantling my book. I haven't actually read it myself (something about waiting like 3 freakin' years for it made me less excited for it when it actually came) but anyway, here it is for all of you. Now you can read this limited edition book :)

Once unzipped, it comes in 3 flavors: ePub, PDF, and the loose JPEGs. And, yes, as a fan, that page saying "buy their shit" had to be there; sorry, but for free you could do a lot worse...

I love MSI and support them and I do buy as much of their shit as I can, but I am also a BT addict and actually started buying their shit *after* torrenting their discography; but yeah, wanted to add here that if you're a fan you should give them some financial support, if you're able. They're cool people.

I'll be seeding as much as I can but sometimes I do have to turn my computer off, anyway hopefully this'll catch on so I won't have to seed forever. If there's anything wrong at all with this torrent please let me know so I can correct it.

~Star_M
